Lisp:reverse-every-other-line.el  --- A mode for genuine bidirectional reading of text by reversing every other line in the visible buffer part.  This mode depends on program 'convert' of the Image Magic-suite.  Comments and improvements welcome.

Git repo: https://github.com/marcowahl/reverse-every-other-line
